rank: #2 in Top Public Universities in America
description:
editorial
Michigan is a highly rated public university located in Ann Arbor, Michigan in the Detroit Area. It is a large institution with an enrollment of 31,319 undergraduate students. Admissions is competitive as the Michigan acceptance rate is 18%. Popular majors include Information Science, Economics, and Business. Graduating 93% of students, Michigan alumni go on to earn a starting salary of $49,800.
